o responded to the incident. He died at the scene.""Police inspected Clyde's 2003 Nissan Altima, and found a suspicious device, which they then detonated using controlled explosions."SOURCES: Dallas News, Corpus Christi Caller Timeshttps://www.dallasnews.com/news/crime/2019/06/17/shots-fired-federal-courthouse-downtown-dallashttps://www.caller.com/story/news/crime/2019/06/17/brian-isaack-clyde-killed-dallas-shooting-went-del-mar-college/1479981001/***]]></description>
